        <p class="person"><strong>mit Martin DWORAK und Gerald KOLLER</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </article>

  <article class="row content-box">
    <h3 class="span12">COACHING + CERTIFICATES (16+16 Einheiten)</h3>

    <div class="span8">
